./docs

# Containerized / CI environments: Podman creates /run/.containerenv, Docker
# creates /.dockerenv (neither exists on a bare-metal host or VM). Inside a
# container, deploy the CLI dotfiles only and skip all host provisioning:
# package installs, /etc system config, GPG/GitHub/Tailscale auth, fonts,
# KDE/GNOME settings, pro-audio realtime provisioning, and the MX Master haptic
# build. The OpenCode workspace build is deliberately KEPT: the agent CLIs are
# first-class here (the OpenCode workspace build soft-skips when its toolchain
# is absent).
#
# distrobox and toolbox are the OPT-OUT: both bind-mount the host $HOME and both
# create /run/.toolboxenv (distrobox touches it for toolbx compatibility), so an
# apply inside one writes to the real host $HOME and must behave like the host —
# provision fully. Skip only a "real" container: a Podman/Docker marker present
# WITHOUT /run/.toolboxenv.
#
# That whole predicate is the `container` fact — declared in .chezmoidata/facts.yaml
# and resolved once in .chezmoitemplates/facts.tmpl, which is also what the guard
# partials and the installers read. The markers are no longer stat'd here: one
# machine, one answer.
{{- $f := includeTemplate "facts.tmpl" . | fromYaml }}
{{- if $f.container }}
.chezmoiscripts/30-linux/*.sh
.chezmoiscripts/20-linux-fedora/*.sh
.chezmoiscripts/40-linux-ubuntu/*.sh
.chezmoiscripts/50-linux-kde/*.sh
.chezmoiscripts/50-linux-gnome/*.sh
.chezmoiscripts/10-auth/*.sh
.chezmoiscripts/80-keys/*.sh
.chezmoiscripts/60-build/*mxm4-haptic.sh
# No MX Master 4 in a container, and the haptic build is skipped just above, so
# the Claude/Codex/AGY haptic plugins and the pi haptic extension have nothing to
# pulse — skip the deployed plugin trees and the pi extension. The generic
# 70-agents/install-agent-plugins.sh script is deliberately KEPT (like the
# dotagents skills install beside it): it still registers compound-engineering
# (marketplace container: keep), while the mxm4-haptic rows are filtered out at
# RENDER time because their marketplaces are container: skip — so there is no
# whole-script skip to make here (the merged basename intentionally does not
# match the former *claude-plugins.sh glob).
.local/share/claude-plugins
.local/share/codex-plugins
.local/share/agy-plugins
.pi/agent/extensions/mxm4-haptic.ts
# The ~/src garden is a host concept: the 80-keys GPG key import is skipped
# above so the encrypted project registry cannot be decrypted here, and the
# 90-src reconcile script (grow/bootstrap/aoe) would have nothing to provision
# and would hard-fail on the then-absent registry — skip both.
.chezmoiscripts/90-src/*.sh
src/garden.yaml
{{- end }}
